title: TytoCare
description:
TytoCare is a telehealth solution that enables a comprehensive medical exam and telehealth visit, anytime and anywhere. 
 
It includes the hand-held Tyto device for examining the heart, lungs, ears, throat, skin, heart rate and temperature, and the TytoCare App for storing exam data, sharing it with a physician, and conducting a live video telehealth exam. By enabling a comprehensive remote exam and visit, TytoCare is greatly expanding the range of conditions that can now be reliably diagnosed via telehealth.
